  "response": "\"Cue the music\" is correct.\n\n*   **Cue** (verb): To signal or prompt an action, especially in a performance. It refers to giving a signal to start something.\n\n*   **Queue** (noun): A line of people or things waiting to be dealt with or served in order. It's related to waiting.\n\nTherefore, in the context of starting music, you're giving a signal or instruction, so \"cue\" is the appropriate word.\n",
